main event: A bright, glowing object estimated to be the size of a house was photographed hovering over a wooded area near Wright Field in August 1964.
interesting points: The object appears to be between the camera and some trees in the foreground, blocking the view of the trees behind it.
The shadows on the ground around the object appear to align correctly with the object's position.
The object is described as being quite different from any known aircraft in the area at the time.
